				<li id="16585316" class="cmnt-root" data="4" data-d="1648783295000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><a class="comment-username" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&u=97276" rel="nofollow"  target="_blank" style="color: #;">Bioautomaton</a></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578523/Battle-Hammer" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">31 Mar 2022 23:21</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16585316" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">For those looking to farm this, I would recommend waiting until you can get a large chunk of Discovery because the walk is pretty long, they are a relatively rare drop, and there&apos;s only one enemy that drops them. I highly recommend the Ash of War &quot;Giant Hunt&quot; as it absolutely demolishes humanoids. I like to chain Giant Hunt -&gt; Charged R2 during ground recovery -&gt; repeat.<br/><br/>Start at West Capital Rampart, turn right and run past the Envoys and avoid the staircase by hugging the right side. They will ignore you. Continue to run forward and right up the hill until you hit a stand of trees and bushes on the left side of the path. Switch to stealth and move to the left side of the path in the trees, but you can continue to run in stealth mode from here. The axe-wielding duelist should be facing away from you as you approach (this is pretty forgiving, but make sure to run the entire time to maintain the pathing timing) and you can sneak past on his left side clambering over the rock pile with no problems. Finally, backstab the hammer-wielding duelist and dispatch him as you please.</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16585316" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16585316" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">0</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>5</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>1</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16585316"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16585316" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16585316"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
